  keywords = {Average Amino Acid Identity,Average Nucleotide Identity,Digital Dna–dna Hybridization,Gammaproteobacteria,Genome Blast Distance Phylogeny,Methanotroph,Methylococcales,Methylotuvimicrobium Gen. Nov.}
